{"tid":1972291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［無得抵賴］WHO既中東冠狀病毒專家都呻：一開始就懷疑人傳人 但俾中國誤導咗","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T01:42:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"238f4af9a4bae1b8212e6d2bc868907850d6457c","tid":1972291,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"WHO Official Says She Suspected Human-To-Human COVID-19 Transmission &lsquo;Right From The Start&rsquo; &mdash; But The WHO Echoed Misleading Chinese Claims To The Contrary For Weeks<br />\n<br />\nA World Health Organization official said Monday that she suspected human-to-human transmission of the novel coronavirus &ldquo;right from the start,&rdquo; beginning on Dec. 31, 2019.<br />\n<br />\nBut WHO officials echoed Chinese authorities and denied any suggestion of human-to-human transmission for weeks after Dec. 31. Chinese doctors, meanwhile, were reported to have known for weeks prior that the virus could be transmitted between humans.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Right from the start, from the first notification we received on the 31st of December, given that this was a cluster of pneumonia &mdash; I&rsquo;m a MERS specialist, so my background is in coronaviruses and influenza &mdash; so immediately thought, given that this is a respiratory pathogen, that of course there may be human-to-human transmission,&rdquo; Dr. Maria Van Kerkhove said in a press briefing Monday.<br />\n<br />\nDespite Van Kerkhove&rsquo;s apparent suspicions, the WHO repeated Chinese authorities&rsquo; downplaying the possibility that the virus could spread between people.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lifetimeuscn/status/1249886251349614593?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifetimeuscn%2Fstatus%2F1249886251349614593%3Fs%3D21&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=3ebc0194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flifetimeuscn%2Fstatus%2F1249886251349614593%3Fs%3D21&h=366272d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lifetimeuscn/status/1249886251349614593?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"6d280440fcc76d0570afe0f040d7ecbbaa089f5d","tid":1972291,"uid":146285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7432cc7fd8f56f32095619179ccf0e22a39946ce","tid":1972291,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54f5ec6d7555cc66fea8050d1d4b4828caba850b","tid":1972291,"uid":212039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"WHO前線係黃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb38e852bd8411907a284f8ee0651ceceb85babb","tid":1972291,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54f5ec6d7555cc66fea8050d1d4b4828caba850b","tid":1972291,"uid":212039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"WHO前線係黃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"唔奇<br />\n中共唔會俾咁多錢買通晒所有人"},{"pid":"c6e57fc1a4756f77ef272e237f816017f1e11184","tid":1972291,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T23:07:21.000Z","msg":"我記得當時佢地投票係兩大極端 一邊好早就話要宣佈大流行<br />\n非洲幫以人數贏左另一邊冇被收買既委員"},{"pid":"4db909089f27092994d042fa431ad9cd8b3b19be","tid":1972291,"uid":66242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T23:22:39.000Z","msg":"其實站在科學求真嘅立場<br />\n唔會人哋講一句就信哂<br />\n而係要睇數據證據再自己 proof<br />\n不過如此有人偽造證據就好難搞<br />\n偽造證據比隨口 up 係大獲好多嘅事"},{"pid":"1301e9a352ee0ef60146e611ae943d103ce4a636","tid":1972291,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T23:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實站在科學求真嘅立場<br />\n唔會人哋講一句就信哂<br 